00:33:32,380 --> 00:33:37,360
 Lord, we thank you so much for this opportunity

619
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:40,120
 and we thank you so much that we are called

620
00:33:40,120 --> 00:33:41,760
 to be your people.

621
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:48,880
 Lord, we pray for each one of us in this room.

622
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:57,000
 We believe that you have a purpose in each one of us.

623
00:33:57,000 --> 00:34:03,620
 You intend us to shine for you

